{"id":"summaries/2020-06-15-dan-stanfield","title":"Dan stanfield","type":"summaries","html":"<p>Title-only contact stub from June 2020 — name \"Dan Stanfield\" captured by <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/yahir-gonzalez\">Yahir</a> with no body. One of many junk-drawer contact stubs from the <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/covid-pandemic-era\">2020 lockdown era</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/yahir-gonzalez\">yahir gonzalez</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/covid-pandemic-era\">covid pandemic era</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/corvallis-or\">corvallis or</a></p>\n","related":[{"id":"entities/corvallis-or","label":"Corvallis, OR"},{"id":"concepts/covid-pandemic-era","label":"COVID Pandemic Era"},{"id":"entities/yahir-gonzalez","label":"Yahir Gonzalez"}]}
